headline: TE Connectivity named among World's Most Ethical Companies for 11th consecutive year
summary: TE Connectivity, a world leader in connectors and sensors, has earned the 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies recognition from Ethisphere, a global leader in defining and advancing the standards of ethical business practices.
